quality dirt road access in beautiful Costilla County, Colorado. If you are looking for land where you can enjoy all of the awesome amenities of beautiful rugged Colorado living, this one checks all the boxes! Whether you\'re looking to build a tiny house, park your RV and camp, or enjoy the hunting, fishing and other recreational activities in the area, this is the perfect place to enjoy it all! Build your dream cabin, or bring your camping gear with you for a short visit and enjoy your summer and chilly winter getaways today!\\u003c/span\\u003e\",\"_content\":\"field_642452df4b3d7\",\"content_block\":\"\",\"_content_block\":\"field_65b9637d43bbe\",\"image_or_gallery\":\"Gallery\",\"_image_or_gallery\":\"field_65b963b343bbf\",\"gallery\":[\"428\",\"443\",\"441\",\"442\",\"440\",\"438\",\"439\",\"437\",\"435\",\"436\",\"434\",\"433\",\"431\",\"432\",\"430\",\"429\"],\"_gallery\":\"field_65b963ff43bc1\"},\"mode\":\"preview\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:acf/content {\"name\":\"acf/content\",\"data\":{\"classes\":\"\",\"_classes\":\"field_63c58e1babc15\",\"style\":\"\",\"_style\":\"field_63c58e07abc14\",\"id\":\"\",\"_id\":\"field_63c58f5259e75\",\"row_classes\":\"\",\"_row_classes\":\"field_63fce04310be4\",\"row_style\":\"\",\"_row_style\":\"field_63fce05810be5\",\"background_image_image_classes\":\"\",\"_background_image_image_classes\":\"field_64137f5e4e069_field_64245ea4e8d5b\",\"background_image_image_style\":\"\",\"_background_image_image_style\":\"field_64137f5e4e069_field_64245eb4e8d5c\",\"background_image_image\":\"\",\"_background_image_image\":\"field_64137f5e4e069_field_64245ebee8d5d\",\"background_image\":\"\",\"_background_image\":\"field_64137ee5e518d\",\"code_block\":\"\",\"_code_block\":\"field_650236497fc5a\",\"column_classes\":\"col-lg-12 text-left\",\"_column_classes\":\"field_642452af4b3d5\",\"column_style\":\"\",\"_column_style\":\"field_642452c34b3d6\",\"content\":\"\\u003cspan\\u003eCostilla County and the surrounding San Luis Valley area offers incredible outdoor recreation:\\u003c/span\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eMt Blanca hiking and 4x4 trails\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eSangre de Cristo Mountain Range\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eRio Grande National Forest\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eGreat Sand Dunes National Park\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eFishing Conejos and Rio Grande rivers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eFishing and camping at dozens of crystal clear mountain lakes.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eHiking and backpacking on 100\'s of miles of trails.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cspan\\u003eATTENTION AGENTS\\u003c/span\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cspan\\u003eWe pay a 5% commission to any Buyer\'s Agent that sells this property. We are not a brokerage, but welcome any and all that would like to do business with Down To Earth Investments.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cspan\\u003eKEY FEATURES\\u003c/span\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003e***Affordable price with direct dirt road access. Many properties in the area do not have direct access\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eLocated only 13 miles north of San Luis in beautiful Costilla County\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eThis property is only 5 miles from Highway 159\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eThis property is also only 35 miles from Alamosa\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eAlamosa is a full service city with good restaurants, a Walmart and a university.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eIn this subdivision you may apply to the state for a well permit - in some of the other Costilla County subdivisions, you must first purchase water rights or not be able to drill a well at all - be careful!\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eIf you\'re an outdoors person, you\'ll find plenty to do here. There\'s enough hiking, biking, hunting, backpacking and fishing opportunities in this part of Colorado to keep you busy for an entire lifetime!\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n \\t\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eExtremely low property taxes could make this an excellent long-term investment.\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003ePAYMENT OPTIONS:\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003e$6,995 (Cash Discount Price)  OR  $10,995 (Payments)\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eTERMS: 0% interest, No Credit check, No Qualifying\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eWe provide our own in house owner-financing.\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eSimple \\u0026amp; Easy.\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eDown Payment = $495\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eAmount Financed = $10,500\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003ePayment Options (choose one):\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003e30 months     $350 per month\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003e42 months     $250 per month\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003e60 months     $175 per month\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eOne time $250 document processing fee\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eNo Prepayment Penalty\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eDiscounts for Early Payoff.\\u003c/b\\u003e\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u003cb\\u003eProperty Tax divi